Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.17,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,THE DAILY LIFE OF A PART-TIME TORTURER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.01,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,NAMANYA SEROMI
