Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.52,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,BUKA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.83,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,HARI INI KAMI TUTUP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.55,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,BONUS
