Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:17.97,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,THE DAILY LIFE OF A PART-TIME TORTURER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.93,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,RUANG ISTIRAHAT
